cc:Work.dc:title: Get SOM - Spread Open Media
cc:Work.dc:description: Here are some banner's I developed for the Spread Open Media movement. I couldn't upload the svg for some reason, but here are the pngs. There are several different ideas here. I like the "Get SOM" slogan. It's catchy and can have several meanings...but is intended to tell people to support open media file types. I'd appreciate any comments
